metadata.name: Split
metadata.description:
A universal feeling, that everybody has felt at least once in his life. As humans, we're able to recover and heal ourselves after big crushes in our lives. Each split always ensues a new beginning.

Split is part of my series "Anatomy of Nature". 

dim. 3000px * 4000px / 600 dpi 
Szabolcs Fekete (@waxxos)
